::: In his diognostic drone body, MEGATRON buzzes around the computer core of 
the Predacon base. He knew Quickstrike was playing with it...but he didnt 
have the codes to access any of the surprizes he left installed. Quickstrike 
would have to get in here himself. And the whole Rat Trap situation was 
getting worse. Megatron just wished he was in his old form so he could rip 
out his spark....but he had to stay hidden, for now. ::::

::: MEGATRON ::: Damn this! Ill have to contact Shredder. Prehaps he has had 
success in finding Quickstrike, however damaged he may be.

::: Looking from left to right he sends a transmission to Shredder ::: Listen 
carefully: Have you found QUickstrike? And If you have I need you to get the 
codes from him...And what is this i hear of the Oblitercons getting involved? 
I never ordered that! Contact me soon. Megatron out.

::: With a burst of static the transmission ended, and all Megatron could do 
now was cater to HELL BEASTs demands. :::
